Introduction

SSAK3 (싹쓰리) is a three-member project co-ed group formed through MBC show "Hangout with Yoo." They released their debut single "Beach Again" on July 18, 2020 and officially debuted on July 25, 2020 with a debut stage on Music Core.

Their Korean name is similar to the word "싹쓸이 (Ssakssuri)" which means to sweep and they want to focus on sweeping the music charts.
